Baby animals of all kinds have distinctive appearances that limit aggression from adults of the same species.  New users should have something similar by their name (like a yellow border) so it is harder to accidentally flame them.  Naturally you have to Tell people to be nice to the newbies but this should make it easier for them to comply.}]